  characterAge: 54
  traitJob: Underground Syndicate Leader
  traitCauseOfDeath: Slipped on a puddle of olive oil while trying to do a cool mobster
    walk
  traitPersonality: Overly dramatic, speaks in a raspy whisper, paranoid about wiretaps
  characterSin: 1
