  propMaterialOverrides: []
  introLines:
  - You come to me... on the day of my afterlife judgment... and ask for paperwork?
  - Keep your voice down. The walls have ears, kid
  answerWhatHappenedBefore: I was walking into my favorite restaurant to collect
    some... protection fees. I hit a patch of freshly spilled extra virgin olive
    oil, my feet went completely airborne, and I landed square on my back
  answerWhatKindOfLife: A life of respect and family values. If people occasionally
    lost their storefronts because they couldn't afford our premium friendship taxes,
    that's just business
  answerWhatWasYourJob: I ran the family operation. We controlled the distribution
    of premium baked goods and controlled the local corner stores with an iron fist
  answerWhatHappenedClothes: This silk shirt is covered in grease and dust because
    I spent twenty minutes rolling around on the restaurant kitchen floor trying
    to scramble back to my feet
  answerWhyHaveItem: This meat cleaver? It's just for... cutting the lasagna. Very
    thick lasagna. You can't blame a businessman for traveling prepared to eat
